OL,5,Clegacy
OL,7,FITV News London has crowned Martin
OL,8,FCosser as our Pride Of Britain
OL,9,Ffundraiser of the Year Award winner,
OL,10,Fas Daisy Busel reports
OL,12,FMartin Cosser made a promise as he
OL,13,Fwatched his teenage son dying in
OL,14,Fhospital, after he'd been stabbed at a
OL,15,Fparty - to spend the rest of my life
OL,16,Feducating young groups of people about
OL,17,Fthe dangers of knife crime.
OL,19,FJust over a year later and he's
OL,20,Falready raised #200,000 for his anti-
OL,21,Fknife crime charity Charlie's Promise.
